        <h2>What is Radon Mitigation?</h2>
        <p>Radon mitigation is the process of reducing radon gas concentrations in your home to safe levels. Our certified professionals install systems that prevent radon from entering your home and remove existing radon gas.</p>

        <h3>How Radon Mitigation Works</h3>
        <p>The most common and effective method is Active Soil Depressurization (ASD), which works by:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Creating a vacuum beneath your home's foundation</li>
          <li>Drawing radon gas from the soil before it enters your home</li>
          <li>Venting the gas safely above your roofline</li>
          <li>Continuously operating to maintain protection</li>
        </ul>

